\b Transformer / Inverter Block\b0\par
\par
For procedures involving transformers or inverters:\par
\bullet  Isolate input and output circuits before servicing\par
\bullet  Allow capacitors to discharge (wait 5 minutes minimum after power-off)\par
\bullet  Check for residual voltage with a properly rated meter\par
\bullet  Document all measurements in the maintenance log\par
\par
